{
  "texts": [
    "In all simulations, we used a flock of 30 birds and a simulation length of 800 steps.",
    "In the case of Hybrid, five of 30 rule-based birds are replaced by LLM-guided birds.",
    "Moreover, each experiment was repeated five times (with different seeds).",
    "The effectiveness of the flocking behavior is evaluated by measuring the distances and angular disparities between birds across the entire simulation.",
    "Statistics for the average amount of steps taken by an ant to find and collect food."
  ]
}